title: #92Noon! 9a Hour 10/27 - Evason/KW/Pasch
description: Cool first hour that features Wild coach Dean Evason in the open, then Vikings great Kevin Williams calls in to celebrate his teammate Jared Allen's Ring of Honor induction, then Cardinals vox Dave Pasch joins with some adversary intel ahead of Sunday's Vikes game!
